title: Yabucoa Fire Station
text:
The Yabucoa Fire Station, at 22 Luis Munoz Rivera St. in <a href="Yabucoa">Yabucoa</a>, <a href="Puerto%20Rico">Puerto Rico</a>, was built in 1943. It was listed on the <a href="National%20Register%20of%20Historic%20Places">National Register of Historic Places</a> in 2013.
It has also been known as Parque de Bombas de Yabucoa.
